{"tid":119312,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[東京] 黎緊同女朋友去東京  想搵迪士尼公主公仔","createTime":"2017-02-13T15:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T09:03:23.000Z","uid":48046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfcc47aeee16625dec33d068d892448009bab841","tid":119312,"uid":48046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"已經唔是第一次同女朋友去<br />\n之前去就比較大路<br />\n淺草雷門寺  上野  秋葉原  台場  涉谷果啲位都去過<br />\n而且上次都去埋箱根<br />\n<br />\n今次去就係散心為主  時間係三月中後期去五日<br />\n女朋友好鐘意迪士尼公主<br />\n想問下咁多位巴打除左Disney / Disney store之外<br />\n有無邊啲位搵到多啲迪士尼嘅公仔或者精品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次就係有啲咩景點可以一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎緊可能會去鐮倉江之島<br />\n西立川踩下單車<br />\n河口湖仲諗緊去唔去好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等過左P牌自駕好似仲正"},{"pid":"d1d2037690ff7490f60f233c29ebcb8344ff6fc1","tid":119312,"uid":48046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:11:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfec423ef90cc1c6c38dabc8145cd22548993fd","tid":119312,"uid":48046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:03:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e126e7fb1f377c3eae9024918c6e3d762a7ee0","tid":119312,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:30:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩日本返黎<br />\n鐮倉江之島河口湖都好值得去<br />\n三個地方都好靚 散心一流"},{"pid":"35c0162152868b2089d3bd7f6b62410c5f079f93","tid":119312,"uid":48046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:03:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩日本返黎<br />\n鐮倉江之島河口湖都好值得去<br />\n三個地方都好靚 散心一流</blockquote><br />\n認真考慮緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}